fields.about:
We are a community of skillful and passionate coders, makers and doers who look for constant improvement by putting their knowledge in practice through great entrepreneurial, technical and engineering events, competitions and conferences.

Our community has a very strong entrepreneurial drive and values – we not only encourage engineers towards being business oriented, innovative and disruptive, but we also promote the incredible engineering culture among non-technical individuals.

Our vision consists on bridging the wide gap between technical and non-technical individuals, as for years, both literally speak completely different languages, and therefore cannot achieve an effective communication. To achieve our vision we have organized events around Europe, including Romania and Slovenia.
